     C***        WWQT2     DIV  W@NQTY    WWPCN   52H
     C           @@QT2     DIV  W@ANS     WWPCN   52H
     C           WWPCN     MULT 100       WPCN2   50
     C           D@PCNT    IFGT *ZERO
     C           WPCN1     ANDGED@PCNT
